Network Speeds
=======================================================

Familiar Speeds in Common Use:

10 Mbps - Ethernet 10BaseT - outmoded

100 Mbps - "Fast Ethernet" - still very common

1000 Mbps - "Gigabit Ethernet or 1Gbps" - typical in new devices

Faster speeds possible but expensive. 

